![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/690def5f-1caa-46c7-814b-b652f8f2f4ea/20240904_171105.jpg?format=original)

Daniel Garcia opens the show looking to fight MJF. MJF is in the crowd.

Garcia tells MJF he wants MJF to get married and have a baby so that they can have an ugly baby. MJF will have to explain to the ugly baby that he used to be a wrestler until Daniel Garcia ended his career.

MJF brings up Daniel Garcia's mother and Garcia rushes out to fight him for that. He catches a swift champagne bottle to the head for his efforts.

MJF says he's going to finish this at All Out.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4192e081-a11f-4dc2-a832-575bbf68e61f/20240904_171918.jpg?format=original)

