*   ## **_CONTINENTAL CHAMPIONSHIP: KAZUCHIKA OKADA DEF. KYLE FLETCHER_**
    

Fantastic match with Fletcher taking Okada to deep waters before Okada hits him with a RANMAKER DICKKICK behind the ref's back right into a regular rainmaker.

Post match, TAKESHITA IS OUT TO CONFRONT OKADA

Fatal Four Way Continental Championship match announced for All Out with the winners being determined on Collision

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7c047cd3-2b4d-46de-a2d7-7317b1fef511/Screenshot_20240904_175426.jpg?format=original)

"I don't care what they say... I think you're a sweet kid."

Jon Moxley to Jack Perry

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c094d140-f893-41eb-bb03-1ad421cf2f15/20240904_175546.jpg?format=original)

Jon Moxley tells the story of the first time he faced Darby Allin. Darby was a kid who lived out of his car, he knew how precious it was to even get onto TV. Because nobody is entitled to even be on TV.

How quickly some people forget that, Moxley says.

DARBY. MOXLEY DOESN'T WANT TO APPLY ANY PRESSURE. Darby.. he just wants to talk.

