Hangman Page and Swerve Strickland's contract signing never happens because Hangman is not here.

He's at Swerve Strickland's childhood home. Hangman talks about Swerve giving him a choice and thinking that he could reason with the man.

Hangman can no longer be reasoned with. He said he would burn down everything Swerve Strickland ever loved. And he meant it?

Say goodbye to whose house? Swerve's....